                    "value": "<p>You adjust your magnetic polarity, causing metal objects to jump and shudder away from you. Attacks made with metal objects against you take a -1 status penalty, and the squares adjacent to you are difficult terrain for creatures wearing metal armor. For creatures made entirely of metal, the penalty to their attack rolls is -2 and the squares adjacent to you are greater difficult terrain.</p>\n<p>While this spell is active, you require an additional Interact action before using a metal object (including to Strike with a metal weapon), and if you're wearing metal armor, you're @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+3)</strong> The status penalty to attack rolls increases by 1.</p>"
